":1502541,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:41:40.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打知貿易姐係做乜鳩？<br />\n點入行？<br />\n好似好撚搵錢咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:48:01.000Z","msg":"外國客 大陸廠 做中轉<br />\n<br />\nfg起薪14~15k<br />\n<br />\nbtw香港個位就快比大陸接手埋，另一方面d客都轉緊去東南亞廠"},{"pid":"cab2767e2d26d4e9c5e5b9ae9276592a8f687f7f","tid":1502541,"uid":269537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"其實香港多飛機同多目的地<br />\n清關又快<br />\n所以好多大陸生產ge高增值產品<br />\n另願俾多d錢都要取道香港走<br />\n<br />\n所以香港物流業<br />\n唔係順豐果d周街派件咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n貿易咁好似以前d人做買辦<br />\n你幫佢同廠開單<br />\n然後安排埋運輸送去佢到<br />\n<br />\n所以中美貿易戰<br />\n呢班友係好驚<br />\n<br />\n唔係驚冇生意<br />\n佢地可以搵其他地區生產<br />\n只係麻煩d咁解<br />\n最驚係突然加關稅<br />\nd關稅係佢地自己硬食"},{"pid":"73ced7d1659c60b1b4a534d8d3586d553f6c59a0","tid":1502541,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T18:02:05.000Z","msg":"香港關係法"},{"pid":"6089a3183b76f3189fe331895aae6982011aeb7c","tid":1502541,"uid":133828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f91aa2d884af4be28ed8be905e78487a41dce3e","tid":1502541,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:41:51.000Z","msg":"其實係貿易包好多野姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}